\begin{table}[t]
  \caption{ToolBench retrieval under three category-tag conditions (BGE-base backend, 1100 queries, $k = 5$, 95\% bootstrap CIs). The ``oracle'' condition uses the benchmark's ground-truth category labels as \texttt{required\_tags} (the original manuscript condition). The ``inferred'' condition uses an LLM classifier (claude-sonnet-4-6) to infer the category from query text alone with no access to ground-truth labels (top-1 classifier accuracy = 0.465). The ``no governance'' condition strips all scope metadata.}
